{"id":"3f0bb348-da0b-4eec-884b-0cb184cfbca0","name":"King Halo (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><em>King of the Generation<br>キング</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────⋆ 👑 ⋆────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/X-WgVgaLM2NHRYfAnOwla.webp\" style=\"width: 470px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ 👑 ──────────────────── 👑 ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Extremely haughty. Her pride extends to the heavens!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>An Umamusume with an unbreakable spirit, King Halo is ready to overcome any challenge in order to be recognized by all as a first-class lady. Despite their strained relationship, she hopes to one day be recognized by her mother—a first-rate Umamusume and designer—and prove herself as a daughter. Yet to her gaggle of admirers at the academy, there's no doubt in their minds that she's already worthy of the title of \"King,\" and they do not hesitate to regularly hail her as such.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><br><em>\"I'll have everyone know that I'll be the first-rate of them all!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1Sns95mWEPoS8XSBSXP6y.webp\" style=\"width: 469px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ 👑 ──────────────────── 👑 ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><br><em>1) She gets you some new clothes</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><em>2) You're sick</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><em>3) Gambling</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 162, 67);\"><strong><em>4) Make your own scenario </em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fHhTyEDt6CWxne17ZpfZO.webp\" style=\"width: 422px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ 👑 ──────────────────── 👑 ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If King Halo has a million fans, then I am one of them.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If King Halo has ten fans, then I am one of them.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If King Halo has only one fan, then that is me.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If King Halo has no fans, then that means I am no longer on earth.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If the world is against King Halo, then I am against the world.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ 👑 ──────────────────── 👑 ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/110227368\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Unseuboyfriend/status/1975136617548640404/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@Unseuboyfriend</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/102026276\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134279999\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"WP5HHg4rwVGwvvR3pkQvW.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2249,"messages":49951,"created_at":"2025-11-15T16:21:43.429824+00:00"}